  "general_provisions": "This bill amends provisions related to school fee waivers.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>limits the number of fee waivers a student may receive;<hr><ltbullet>requires local education agencies to establish a cap on fee waivers;<hr><ltbullet>allows a student to request a fee waiver for a second trip; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
